decide which posts appear in your feed (based on posts you’ve liked in the past).\n\nAdditionally, it would be great to get a notification when someone forks or comments on one of my posts.  Keeping these out of the web interface but putting them in an App may be a way to maintain those FedWiki tenets while still offering notifications for those who want them.\n\nI can picture using the App to catch up on what’s happening in my FedWiki community while I’m waiting in line, and also using it side-by-side with the web version.\n"
